title: Jack Van Impe - The New World Order (VIDEO)
description:
30 minutes to change YOUR eternity! Shocking revelations from current events and the Word of God!

In this astonishing 30-minute video experience from Drs. Jack and Rexella Van Impe you will discover:

-What is the New World Order and why should you be concerned?

-The names of well-known leaders and organizations behind the New World Order!

-Who Henry Kissinger says is in a position to lead the New World Order! Is it our President?

-Who has taken control of the European Union? Is it Obama?

-What the Bible says about development of this New World Order.

-What event announces that the Messiah is about to return to set up His Kingdom here on earth!

-And much more!
